Subject: Re: [T2] Paint new trailer to match my bus?

If you're going to rattle-can it, at least "scuff" the existing paint with
sandpaper. Then go over it with a couple coats of primer (O Reilly's carries
a high-build variety that works well). Then lay the finish coat(s) over the
primer... should work okay.
